| `sweep-runtime` | `{{SWEEP_RUNTIME_PATH}}` | Startup + 5-min sweep (stale handoffs, log rotate, queue integrity, disk check) |
| `log-tool-use` | `{{LOG_TOOL_USE_PATH}}` | PostToolUse hook handler — appends to `{{TOOL_USE_LOG_PATH}}` |
| `backoff.sh` | `{{BACKOFF_HELPER_PATH}}` | Shared exponential-backoff helper |
